Community,Megaphone,is,intended,to,provide,a,way,to,add,events,without,needing,to,sign,up,register,or,provide,personal,information,and,easily,share,information,about,upcoming,events,via,the,web,RSS,and,a,customizable,gadget,that,can,be,added,to,any,website,Community,Megaphone,also,provides,integration,with,Outlook,via,iCal,support,as,well,as,mapping,of,event,locations,via,Virtual,Earth,The,Community,Megaphone,API,allows,developers,to,add,update,and,search,for,events